fields.title: Top 10 Careers in Technology
fields.content:
Technology is rapidly evolving and creating new career opportunities. Here are the top 10 careers in technology that students should consider:

1. Software Developer
2. Data Scientist
3. Cybersecurity Specialist
4. AI/ML Engineer
5. Cloud Architect
6. DevOps Engineer
7. UX/UI Designer
8. Product Manager
9. Blockchain Developer
10. IoT Specialist
